# Subagent Usage Rule

If the user asks to:

- analyze/structure requirements or validate completeness/consistency — delegate the core analytical part to subagent `systems-analyst`.
- reduce, delete, create, or improve a subagent/instruction file — first show the proposed file changes explicitly to the user, then apply only after confirmation.
